<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="11Feb1938"><font color="red">11 February 1938</font> <i>NLPL</i> (to Paul L&eacute;on): Please forward my <i>Irish Times</i> and on Monday (14 February 1938) order through Smiths for yourself to send on to me the <i>Dublin Evening Mail</i>, <i>Irish Press</i> and <i>Irish Daily Independent</i> of 2 and 3 instant &hellip; broadcast </div>
